-- Seymour Pierce to Be Sold to East European Buyer, Telegraph Says
-- B y   Z i j i n g   W u
-- 2012-07-01T08:08:42Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-07-01/seymour-pierce-to-be-sold-to-east-european-buyer-telegraph-says.html
Seymour Pierce Ltd., the British
small-cap stockbroker, was sold with conditions to a firm from
either the Ukraine or  Kazakhstan , the  Sunday Telegraph  reported,
without saying where it obtained the information.  The deal is subject to approval from the Financial Services
Authority, the newspaper said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
